1. *Ostavi* ga na miru! (Leave him alone!) 
2. On je *ostavio* svoj dom. (He left his home.)
3. Nisam *ostavila* nikakve tragove. (I didn't leave any traces.)
4. On je *ostavio* lepu poruku. (He left a nice message.)
5. Ono što je *ostavio* nije bilo bitno. (What he left was not important.) 
6. *Ostavio* je dugove za sobom. (He left debts behind.) 
7. Ona je *ostavila* mnogo para za nas. (She left a lot of money for us.) 
8. Ona je *ostavila* svoj život za porodicu. (She left her life for her family.)